{"tid":2064574,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"內地70個大中城市新建住宅售價按月升0.5%","createTime":"2020-06-15T02:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T02:12:02.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d9f2d10d2f77e4ae96f2d848ac034cba96277c","tid":2064574,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"內地70個大中城市新建住宅售價按月升0.5%<br />\n2020-06-15 HKT 09:49<br />\n<br />\n內地公布70個大中城市新建住宅銷售價格指數，據外電測算，按年上升4.9%，升幅較4月收窄0.2個百分點，按月就上升0.5%，升幅與4月相同。<br />\n<br />\n國家統計局公布，上月北京、上海、廣州同深圳新建商品住宅銷售價格按月上升0.7%，升幅較4月擴大0.5個百分點；按年上升2.9%，與4月時相同。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532077-20200615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532077-20200615.htm&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8pnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=f26db583\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532077-20200615.htm&h=3e244e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532077-20200615.htm</a>"}]}